ages of Scotland">Scotland</a>&#160;•</span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Languages_of_Wales" title="Languages of Wales" class="mw-redirect">Wales</a>)</span></small><span style="white-space:nowrap">&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Languages_of_Vatican_City" title="Languages of Vatican City">Vatican City</a></span></p>
