uages_of_Crimea" title="Languages of Crimea" class="mw-redirect">Crimea</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Languages_of_Dagestan&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Languages of Dagestan (page does not exist)">Dagestan</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Languages_of_the_Faroe_Islands" title="Languages of the Faroe Islands">Faroe Islands</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Languages_of_Gagauzia&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Languages of Gagauzia (page does not exist)">Gagauzia</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Languages_of_Gibraltar" title="Languages of Gibraltar">Gibraltar</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Languages_of_Guernsey" title="Languages of Guernsey" class="mw-redirect">Guernsey</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Languages_of_Ingushetia&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Languages of Ingushetia (page does not exist)">Ingushetia</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Languages_of_Jan_Mayen" title="Languages of Jan Mayen" class="mw-redirect">Jan Mayen</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Languages_of_Jersey" title="Languages of Jersey">Jersey</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Languages_of_Kabardino-Balkaria&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Languages of Kabardino-Balkaria (page does not exist)">Kabardino-Balkaria</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Languages_of_Kalmykia&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Languages of Kalmykia (page does not exist)">Kalmykia</a>&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Language